credit_line: Gift of the National Academy of Design from the Mrs. William T. Brewster Bequest
title: Tree Covered Hillside Looking toward Harbor Town and Ocean
provenance: Anna Richards Brewster, Scarsdale, NY, 1905-1952; William T. Brewster,
description: View from hilltop. In lower left, outline of a bridge with (possible) train, a series of two tree-topped hills. Behind hills, in center of composition, outlines of town on shoreline. Across the river (possible) outlines of more structures.
name: Sketchbook folio
